Entries.default: "It is folly to stand against a watershaper adept."
"When all of the masters gather in Neketaka, our enemies will know their doom."
"Friends of the Huana have nothing to fear from us."
"An absent dragon does not diminish our power."
"The dragon's spirit is a crutch for students. We are beyond such things."
"Your Rauataian allies will deceive you. Listen to nothing they say."
"Anyone who sails under a pirate's flag will suffer a pirate's fate."
"Greed is a powerful force in these waters. But there are greater forces, I say."
"Ngati's chosen shares your path? Beware of his protective mother."
